<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Package Has Been Created</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #fff8f2; color: #333; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #800020 60%, #D4AF37 100%); color: #fff; padding: 24px 0; text-align: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .content { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; margin: 32px auto; max-width: 480px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px #80002022; }
    .label { color: #D4AF37; font-weight: bold; }
    .tracking { font-size: 1.3em; color: #800020; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { color: #800020; text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; font-size: 0.95em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <span class="logo">DropSecure</span>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2 style="color:#800020;">Package Created Successfully</h2>
    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Your package has been created and is now being processed.</p>
    <p class="label">Tracking Number:</p>
    <div class="tracking"><%= trackingNumber %></div>
    <p><%= packageDetails %></p>
    <p>We'll keep you updated as your package moves through our network.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> DropSecure. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>